OL,3,CFarmers warn cost of growing food will
OL,4,Chit consumers down the line
OL,6,FA farmer has told UTV that fuel and
OL,7,Ffertiliser prices have increased
OL,8,Fdramatically since the conflict began
OL,9,Fin Iran, with concerns over whether he
OL,10,Fwill break even on this year's cereal
OL,11,Fcrop.
OL,13,FDespite the newly-agreed ceasefire,
OL,14,Fconcerns remain among community about
OL,15,Fthe conflict's lasting effects.
OL,17,F"Going forward this year, our costs
OL,18,Fhave nearly doubled, is the end
OL,19,Fproduct going to be double? That's
OL,20,Fwhat nobody knows, that's the gamble,"
OL,21,Fsaid Co Armagh farmer David Kane.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
