OL,3,CFarmers warn cost of growing food will
OL,4,Chit consumers down the line
OL,6,FWith the Strait of Hormuz - that vital
OL,7,Fshipping corridor for much of the
OL,8,Fworld's oil - closed off, demand has
OL,9,Fbeen put on other resources.
OL,11,FIt has meant fuel prices have put a
OL,12,Ftighter pinch on some pockets,
OL,13,Fincluding farmers.
OL,15,FThe Ulster Farmers' Union has now
OL,16,Fwritten to the government to highlight
OL,17,Fconcerns felt by David and many others
OL,18,Facross Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
