OL,3,CFarmers warn cost of growing food will
OL,4,Chit consumers down the line
OL,6,FUFU President William Irvine said:
OL,7,F"The real risk here is that this is
OL,8,Fgoing to prompt food inflation for our
OL,9,Fconsumers."
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the government said
OL,12,Fit is monitoring the potential impact
OL,13,Fof the conflict on the food and
OL,14,Ffarming sector.
OL,16,FThey added that they expect no change
OL,17,Fto food availability and will continue
OL,18,Fto meet with stakeholders, including
OL,19,Funions.
